<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <title>{{ datetime }} 学习反馈 « 传智播客•黑马程序员</title>
  <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="data:image/png;base64,">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.min.css">
</head>

<body>
  <div class="page">
    <h1 class="page-header">{{ datetime }} 学习反馈</h1>
    <h5 class="title">亲爱的同学：</h5><p class="paragraph">为了全面提高教育质量，请你们对今天的课程学习目标作出实事求是的反馈。请对下列问题作出适当地回答。</p>
    <hr>
    <h5 class="title">反馈信息：</h5>

    <form action="/{{ stamp }}" method="post">
      <div class="meta row">
        <div class="col-md-6"><span>姓名：</span><input id="name" type="text" name="name" placeholder="请输入你的姓名（必填）" autocomplete="off"></div>
        <div class="col-md-5"></div>
        <div class="col-md-4"><span>评估时间：</span><strong>{{ datetime }}</strong></div>
      </div>
      <ol id="targets" class="questions">
        {{#each(targets)}}
        <li>
          <h6{{#if(this.highlight)}} style="color: #f40"{{/if}}>{{ this.question }}{{#if(this.highlight)}}（重点）{{/if}}</h6>
          <div class="row">
            {{#each(answer_options, 'option', 'i')}}
            <label class="col-md-3"><input type="radio" name="{{../xindex}}" value="{{i}}">{{option.full}}</label>
            {{/each}}
          </div>
        </li>
        {{/each}}
      </ol>
      <hr>
      <h5 class="title">其他意见或建议：</h5>
      <textarea class="form-control" name="note" cols="160" rows="8" placeholder="相信您的建议一定可以一针见血（不支持富文本）"></textarea>
      <input id="hash" type="hidden" name="hash" value="272f6c7405e57d101574f2cd39ff2284">
      <p class="text-danger">注意：每人只能提交一次，请认真填写后再提交！</p>
      <button id="btn" type="submit">确认提交</button>
    </form>
  </div>
  <script src="/script.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
